OL,3,CWatch as bear rescued from tree after
OL,4,Cwandering into residential street
OL,6,FThe bear had likely wandered into the
OL,7,Fneighbourhood in search of food, but
OL,8,Fclimbed a tree when it became nervous
OL,9,Fof its surroundings.
OL,11,FWildlife and law enforcement officials
OL,12,Fcame to rescue the bear after it had
OL,13,Fbeen up in the branches for around
OL,14,Ffour hours, and they successfully
OL,15,Fcaught it in a net stretched beneath
OL,16,Fthe tree.
OL,18,FThe bear will now be released back
OL,19,Finto the wild.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
